CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 14, 1945, pg. 19 reads: "I'm Two - So says little Gwendolyn Morris, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Claude Morris, of Chauncey Drive, who celebrated her second birthday recently. Many of her playmates gathered to help her celebrate the important day. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of birthday party with three boys, and seven girls, including Gwendolyn Morris, posed behind her birthday cake, gathered in living room of Mr. and Mrs. Claude Morris, Chauncey Drive, another pose
